Package Control Messages
========================

SublimeLinter-contrib-standard
------------------------------

  SublimeLinter-contrib-standard
  -------------------------------
  This linter plugin for SublimeLinter provides an interface to standard.
  
  ** IMPORTANT! **
  
  Before this plugin will activate, you *must*
  follow the installation instructions here:
  
  https://github.com/Flet/SublimeLinter-contrib-standard
  
  Want to automatically format your text? 
  Install StandardFormat from package control!
  (https://github.com/bcomnes/sublime-standard-format)


StandardFormat
--------------

  Standard Format
  ---------------
  This auto-formatter requires that you install `standard` in order to function properly:
  
    $ npm i standard -g
  
  Please file any issues with the plug-in you come across at:
  
    https://github.com/bcomnes/sublime-standard-format/issues
  
  Auto-formatting issues can be directed at:
  
    https://github.com/feross/standard/issues
  
  Please view the README for more information/documentation.
  
  Consider installing the `standard` linter plug-in:
  
    https://github.com/Flet/SublimeLinter-contrib-standard
